function test() {
  if (true) {
    var x = 10;
    let y = 20;
    const z = 30;
  }
  console.log(x); // ✅ 10
  try { console.log(y); } catch (e) { console.log("Error for y:", e.message); } // ✅ "y is not defined"
  try { console.log(z); } catch (e) { console.log("Error for z:", e.message); } // ✅ "z is not defined"
}
test();
```

פלט צפוי:
```
10
Error for y: y is not defined
Error for z: z is not defined
```

אם הפלט הזה מופיע – הפתרון נכון.

